{"word":"στιβάς","slug":"στιβάς","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>στιβάς</b></el> <el>(στῐβάς, άδος,) </el><br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:στείβω'><el>στείβω</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li750'><b>1. </b><i>a bed of straw, rushes</i>, or <i>leaves</i>, <b><a href='S:Euripides'>Eur.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Theocritus'>Theocr.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><i>a mattress, pallet</i>, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Aristophanes'>Ar.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}